{"s":"church-yard-sign","img":"yard-sign.jpg","badge":"New","cat":"Signs & Signage","name":"Church Yard Sign","tag":"Weatherproof yard signs for service times, events, and outreach.","verse":"He has anointed me to proclaim good news to the poor","ref":"Luke 4:18","specs":[("Material","4.5mm Corrugated Plastic"),("Weight","1100gsm"),("UV Resistance","12 months"),("Shape","Custom cut available"),("Hardware","Wire H-stake or frame")],"feats":["Weatherproof — rain, heat, and cold resistant","12-month UV resistance outdoors","Custom cut shapes — arrows, crosses, and more","Wire H-stake included for easy lawn installation","Lightweight and reusable season after season"],"desc":["Church yard signs are one of the most cost-effective ways to communicate with your surrounding community. Place them along the street before a special service, in members yards, or along walkways to guide visitors.","Made from 4.5mm thick corrugated plastic (Coroplast), these signs are weatherproof and lightweight. Wire H-stakes push directly into the ground — no tools required. UV-resistant printing keeps your design sharp for up to 12 months.","We offer custom cut shapes alongside standard rectangles — cross-shaped signs and directional arrows are popular choices. Full-color print on one or both sides."],"uc":[("📢","Street-side service announcements"),("🎉","VBS and event promotion"),("🤝","Community outreach programs"),("🎄","Holiday service notifications"),("📍","Directional signage for events"),("🏘️","Member lawn displays")],"sizes":["12x18 in","18x24 in","24x36 in","Custom"]},
{"s":"acrylic-pvc-sign","img":"acrylic-sign.jpg","badge":"Premium","cat":"Signs & Signage","name":"Acrylic & PVC Sign","tag":"Rigid, professional-grade signs for permanent church use.","verse":"Trust in the Lord with all your heart","ref":"Proverbs 3:5","specs":[("Materials","PVC or Acrylic"),("Thickness","2mm to 20mm"),("Print","UV printing — permanent bond"),("Shape","Any custom shape"),("Finish","Gloss or matte")],"feats":["UV printing bonded permanently to rigid material","PVC (budget) or Acrylic (premium clarity)","Custom shapes — crosses, shields, arches","Thickness from 2mm to 20mm","Professional standoff mounting available"],"desc":["Acrylic and PVC signs bring a level of permanence and professionalism that fabric and paper simply cannot match. These are the signs you install once and leave — on walls, doors, welcome desks, hallways, and exterior facades.","We print directly onto the rigid material using UV printing, which bonds ink permanently to the surface. PVC is our budget-friendly option for most indoor applications. Acrylic offers premium glass-like clarity for lobby nameplates and decorative wall pieces.","Both materials can be cut to custom shapes. Cross-shaped plaques, shield crests, arched nameplates, and directional signs are all achievable. Thickness ranges from 2mm to 20mm."],"uc":[("🏛️","Church name & address plaques"),("🚪","Room & ministry labels"),("🤝","Welcome desk nameplates"),("📍","Directional & wayfinding signs"),("🏆","Memorial & honor plaques"),("📸","Decorative scripture wall art")],"sizes":["Custom — any size up to 4x8 ft"]},
{"s":"church-vinyl-sticker","img":"sticker.jpg","badge":"Giveaway Favorite","cat":"Stickers & Magnets","name":"Church Vinyl Sticker","tag":"Custom die-cut stickers with crosses, scripture, and logos — perfect for outreach.","verse":"In all things God works for the good of those who love Him","ref":"Romans 8:28","specs":[("Material","UV-resistant vinyl"),("Print","Full-color"),("Cut","Custom die-cut or standard"),("Finish","Gloss or matte"),("Min. Order","25 units")],"feats":["Custom die-cut to any shape — crosses, doves, shields","UV-resistant for outdoor surfaces","Full-color printing for vibrant religious designs","Great for bulk giveaways at events and outreach","Apply to Bibles, laptops, water bottles, car bumpers"],"desc":["Vinyl stickers are one of the most versatile and affordable outreach tools available. A well-designed sticker with your church logo, a memorable scripture, or a bold cross graphic becomes a mini billboard wherever it is placed.","Our stickers are printed in full color on durable UV-resistant vinyl. Custom die-cutting lets us produce any shape — a traditional cross, a descending dove, a shield, a fish symbol, or your church emblem.","Stickers are extremely popular as giveaways at VBS, youth events, revivals, and community outreach programs. Inexpensive enough to give away freely and impactful enough to leave a lasting impression."],"uc":[("🎁","Event & VBS giveaways"),("📖","Bible & journal decoration"),("🚗","Car bumper & window stickers"),("💻","Laptop & device stickers"),("🤝","Outreach kits & welcome bags"),("🏫","Youth group merchandise")],"sizes":["1x1 in","2x2 in","3x3 in","4x4 in","Custom"]},
{"s":"window-transfer-decal","img":"window-decal.jpg","badge":"Clean Look","cat":"Stickers & Magnets","name":"Window Transfer Decal","tag":"Letter-only window decals for a clean, professional church presence.","verse":"Whatever you do, do it all in the name of the Lord Jesus","ref":"Colossians 3:17","specs":[("Type","Transfer vinyl — no background"),("Thickness","100 microns"),("UV Resistance","3-5 years"),("Application","Glass, windows, smooth surfaces"),("Color","Custom")],"feats":["Letters and shapes only — no background film visible","Applied directly to glass for a professional look","UV resistant for 3-5 years","Perfect for church name, service times, and scripture","Clean removal without residue when needed"],"desc":["Transfer decals give your church windows and glass doors a clean, permanent-looking display without the boxed-in appearance of a standard sticker. Because there is no background film — just the lettering and graphics — the result looks like text is printed directly on the glass.","Ideal for displaying your church name on the front door, listing service times on a window, applying scripture to a glass partition, or labeling ministry rooms with elegant vinyl lettering.","At 100 microns thick, our transfer decals are durable enough for outdoor glass while remaining cleanly removable if your messaging ever needs to change."],"uc":[("🚪","Front door & entrance glass"),("🕐","Service times display"),("📖","Scripture on glass partitions"),("🏛️","Church name & address"),("🏢","Office & ministry room labels"),("🪟","Storefront & lobby windows")],"sizes":["Custom — any size"]},
{"s":"floor-decal","img":"floor-sticker.jpg","badge":"Durable","cat":"Stickers & Magnets","name":"Floor Decal","tag":"Waterproof, slip-resistant floor graphics that guide and inspire your congregation.","verse":"Make level paths for your feet and take only ways that are firm","ref":"Proverbs 4:26","specs":[("Material","Vinyl with anti-slip laminate"),("UV Resistance","Yes"),("Waterproof","Yes"),("Abrasion Resistance","High — foot traffic rated"),("Size","Any size")],"feats":["Anti-slip laminate for safety compliance","Waterproof — suitable for entryways","High abrasion resistance — built for foot traffic","Full-color printing in any design","Custom shapes including crosses, circles, arrows"],"desc":["Floor decals are an often-overlooked but highly effective form of church signage. Placed at key decision points, floor graphics guide visitors intuitively toward the sanctuary, restrooms, children's ministry, or welcome desk.","Beyond wayfinding, floor decals can be used creatively — a scripture verse at the entrance, a cross motif in the lobby, or dove-styled directional arrows leading families to the children's area.","Our floor decals include an anti-slip laminate layer for safety. They are waterproof and abrasion-resistant, suitable for entryways and interior spaces alike. Any size and shape is available."],"uc":[("🧭","Wayfinding & directional arrows"),("✝️","Decorative cross motifs"),("📖","Scripture verse displays"),("🏛️","Lobby welcome graphics"),("👶","Children's area markers"),("🤸","Youth & recreation spaces")],"sizes":["Custom — any size and shape"]},
{"s":"church-fridge-magnet","img":"magnet.jpg","badge":"Giveaway","cat":"Stickers & Magnets","name":"Church Fridge Magnet","tag":"Custom fridge magnets with service info, prayer guides, and church contact details.","verse":"I can do all this through Him who gives me strength","ref":"Philippians 4:13","specs":[("Thickness","0.3mm / 0.5mm / 0.7mm / 0.9mm"),("Shape","Any shape"),("Print","Full-color"),("Feature","Removable & writable"),("Min. Order","50 units")],"feats":["Full-color printing of your church branding","Service times, address, and phone on one piece","Writable surface — members can add personal notes","Four thickness options","Custom cut to any shape — cross, shield, house"],"desc":["Church refrigerator magnets are a classic and practical giveaway. Every time a congregation member opens their fridge, they see your church name, service times, phone number, and whatever message you choose to include.","Popular designs include weekly scripture verses, prayer request phone lines, service schedule cards, and holiday greetings. The writable surface allows members to jot notes directly on the magnet.","Available in four thickness options. Custom cut shapes — a cross, a church building silhouette, or a simple rectangle — add a distinctive touch that sets your magnets apart."],"uc":[("🎁","New member welcome kits"),("📅","Service schedule reminders"),("🙏","Prayer guide giveaways"),("🎄","Christmas & holiday gifts"),("📞","Church contact info cards"),("🏘️","Community outreach packages")],"sizes":["Business card size","4x6 in","Custom"]},
{"s":"magnetic-car-sign","img":"car-magnet.jpg","badge":"Mobile Ministry","cat":"Stickers & Magnets","name":"Magnetic Car Sign","tag":"Removable magnetic signs for church vehicles — spread your message on every road.","verse":"How beautiful are the feet of those who bring good news","ref":"Romans 10:15","specs":[("Thickness","0.5mm / 0.7mm / 0.9mm"),("Print","Full-color"),("Shape","Any shape"),("UV Resistance","Yes"),("Removable","Yes — no residue")],"feats":["Removable and reusable — no adhesive residue","UV-resistant and waterproof for outdoor use","Full-color print of your church logo and message","Holds firmly to any magnetic metal vehicle surface","Easy to swap between vehicles as needed"],"desc":["Magnetic car signs turn your personal or church vehicle into a moving advertisement for your ministry. Every drive across town is an opportunity for your congregation to represent your church in the community.","Unlike vinyl decals, magnetic signs are fully removable and leave zero residue. A church member can promote the ministry during the week and remove the sign for personal use on weekends.","Our magnets are UV-resistant and fully waterproof, handling daily driving conditions without fading or deteriorating."],"uc":[("🚗","Personal member vehicles"),("🚐","Church van & bus fleet"),("🤝","Community event promotion"),("📢","Revival & event announcements"),("🌍","Mission trip vehicles"),("🏘️","Neighborhood outreach")],"sizes":["12x18 in","18x24 in","Custom"]},
{"s":"car-van-wrap","img":"vehicle-wrap.jpg","badge":"High Impact","cat":"Stickers & Magnets","name":"Car / Van Wrap","tag":"Full and partial vehicle wraps that transform your church vehicle into a rolling ministry.","verse":"You will be my witnesses to the ends of the earth","ref":"Acts 1:8","specs":[("Material","140gsm Cast Vinyl"),("Print","Eco / UV Ink"),("UV Resistance","3-5 years"),("Coverage","Full or partial wrap"),("Finish","Gloss or matte")],"feats":["3-5 year UV resistance — built for long-term use","Full or partial wrap options to fit any budget","140gsm cast vinyl conforms to vehicle curves","Bold full-color church branding and scripture","Protects original paint — removes cleanly"],"desc":["A vehicle wrap is the highest-impact mobile advertising available. Studies show a wrapped vehicle generates 30,000-70,000 impressions per day in urban environments. For a church van, pastor's car, or ministry vehicle, that is an extraordinary daily reach.","Our 140gsm cast vinyl wraps conform to the contours of any vehicle without bubbles or lifting. UV-resistant for 3-5 years, and removes cleanly without damaging original paint when it is time for a change.","Full wraps cover the entire vehicle. Partial wraps — covering just the doors, rear, or one side panel — still deliver strong visual impact at a more accessible cost."],"uc":[("🚐","Church van & shuttle fleet"),("🚗","Pastor's personal vehicle"),("🚌","Youth ministry bus"),("🏘️","Community visibility & branding"),("🌍","Mission trip vehicles"),("📢","Event announcement vehicles")],"sizes":["Full wrap","Half wrap","Partial (doors / rear)","Custom"]},
{"s":"church-flyer-bulletin","img":"flyer.jpg","badge":"Church Staple","cat":"Print & Paper","name":"Church Flyer & Bulletin","tag":"Full-color church bulletins, event flyers, and service programs on premium paper.","verse":"Preach the word; be prepared in season and out of season","ref":"2 Timothy 4:2","specs":[("Sizes","A5, A4, A3, Custom"),("Paper Weights","120g, 157g, 180g, 200g, 250g"),("Print","Full-color, both sides"),("Finish","Gloss or matte"),("Turnaround","Same-day available")],"feats":["Five paper weight options from 120g to 250g","Full-color printing on both sides","Available in A5, A4, and A3 sizes","Gloss finish for vibrant photography","Same-day production for Sunday emergencies"],"desc":["The church bulletin is one of the most enduring forms of church communication — and a well-designed one makes a real difference in how your congregation experiences a service. From order of worship to announcements, the bulletin ties a service together.","Beyond weekly bulletins, we produce event flyers for revivals, concerts, VBS, community outreach programs, and church anniversaries. Five paper weight options from an everyday 120g sheet to premium 250g card stock.","All orders are printed in full color on both sides. Same-day production is available — because we understand that church is Sunday and deadlines are real."],"uc":[("📋","Weekly service bulletins"),("🎉","Event flyers & invitations"),("📅","Ministry calendars"),("🙏","Prayer & devotional cards"),("🎭","Service & ceremony programs"),("📢","Community outreach flyers")],"sizes":["A5 (5.8x8.3 in)","A4 (8.3x11.7 in)","A3 (11.7x16.5 in)","Custom"]},
